# ðŸ’» DESKTOP PRODUCT PAGE - Visual Reference Description

## ROUTE
`/product/[id]`

## VIEWPORT
Desktop and tablets: 768px and above

---

## REFERENCE WEBSITES TO STUDY

**Primary References:**
1. **SHEIN Desktop Website** - Product detail page
2. **Shopee Desktop Website** - Product detail page
3. **Amazon Product Page** - Layout reference

Study how these platforms organize product information on larger screens.

---

## EXISTING LAKU LAYOUT TO PRESERVE

**Your Current Desktop App Has:**
- A fixed left sidebar with the LAKU logo at the top
- Navigation items below the logo: Beranda, Video, Pesan, Keranjang, Profil, Lainnya
- The sidebar is about 15% of the screen width
- A search bar at the top of the main content area
- The main content area to the right of the sidebar showing a 3-4 column product grid
- Product cards with red prices, gray struck-through original prices, and "X+ terjual" format

**The product page should work WITHIN this existing layout, not replace it.**

---

## OVERALL LAYOUT CONCEPT

**SHEIN does this perfectly:**

When you visit a SHEIN product page, you see:
- Their navigation sidebar on the left (like your Laku sidebar - this stays)
- The main content area takes up the rest of the screen
- Within that main content area, the product page uses a two-column layout:
  - Left column (60% width): Product images
  - Right column (40% width): Product information that sticks as you scroll

**This is the pattern to follow - a layout WITHIN your main content area.**

---

## MAIN CONTENT AREA STRUCTURE

The product page renders in the space to the right of your existing Laku sidebar.

### At the Top (Header Area)
In the area where your search bar currently is, add:
- Breadcrumb navigation: "Home > Category > Product Name"
- Keep the search bar
- Add a share button or icon
- Keep your existing header structure

### Two-Column Layout (Main Content)

**LEFT COLUMN (60% of content area):**

**Vertical Thumbnail Strip:**
On the far left side of this column is a narrow vertical strip showing small thumbnail images of all product photos. Each thumbnail is:
- About 80-100 pixels square
- Stacked vertically with small gaps between them
- Has a border - the active thumbnail has a red or bold border
- Shows 5-6 thumbnails visible at once
- Can scroll if there are more than 6 images
- When you click a thumbnail, the main image changes

**SHEIN shows this:** Vertical thumbnails on the left, main image on the right.

**Main Product Image:**
To the right of the thumbnail strip is the large main product image:
- Square or slightly portrait aspect ratio
- High quality, detailed product photo
- When you hover over it with your mouse, it zooms in slightly or shows a zoom cursor
- Clicking it opens a fullscreen lightbox gallery
- Smooth transition when switching between images
- Shows which image you're viewing like "1/5" in a corner badge

**RIGHT COLUMN (40% of content area):**

This column contains all the product information and should "stick" as you scroll - meaning as you scroll down the page, this column stays visible until you reach the reviews section.

**Sticky Behavior:**
- When the page first loads, the right column is at the top
- As you scroll down, this column sticks to the top of the viewport
- It stops sticking when you scroll far enough to reach the reviews section
- This allows you to see product info while scrolling through images or description

---

## RIGHT COLUMN CONTENT (Top to Bottom)

### Badges and Labels
At the very top, small badges like:
- "Trends" in purple background
- "Choice" in black background  
- Other promotional badges
These are small pill-shaped elements in a row.

### Product Title
Below badges, the product title in large, bold text:
- 24-28 pixels font size
- Bold weight
- Black color
- Can wrap to 2-3 lines
- Example: "Elegant Floral Maxi Dress - Summer Collection 2024"

### SKU and Rating Row
Below the title, small text showing:
- SKU number: "sku: sm2507119482691158"
- Separator: " | "
- Star rating (5 stars, filled according to rating)
- Review count as a link: "109+ Reviews"
- Clicking the review count scrolls to reviews section

### Price Section
Very prominent pricing display:
- Current price: LARGE (36-40px), BOLD, RED text
- Format: "Rp299,000"
- Original price next to it: smaller (20px), GRAY, struck through "Rp399,000"
- Discount badge: pill shape, red background, white text "-25%"
- Payment info below: "Pay now in 4 payments of Rp4,000..." in small text

### Bestseller Badge (if applicable)
A prominent badge or banner:
- "#2 Bestseller in Casual - Basic Men Sweatpants"
- With category icon
- Clickable to go to category
- Stands out visually

### Variant Selection

**Color Selection:**
- Label: "Color: [Selected Color Name]"
- "Large Image" link on the right to view color in detail
- Color swatches in a horizontal row:
  - Each swatch 50-60 pixels
  - Square or circle
  - Shows actual color or product image in that color
  - Selected color has thick red border
  - Others have thin gray border
  - Hover shows preview

**Size Selection:**
- Label: "Size [US Size]" with size system dropdown
- Grid of size buttons (4-5 per row):
  - Each button shows size (e.g., "S", "M", "L")
  - Also shows conversion like "S (36)"
  - Selected size: red background, white text
  - Available sizes: white background, black text, gray border
  - Out of stock: grayed out, diagonal line through
  - Hover effect on available sizes
- Links below: "Size Guide" and "Check My Size"

**Quantity Selector:**
- Label: "Quantity"
- Horizontal control:
  - Minus button | Number input field | Plus button
  - Clean, bordered design
  - Plus/minus disabled when at limits

### Action Buttons

**Add to Cart Button:**
- Very prominent and wide (takes up 75-80% of column width)
- Height: 50-56 pixels
- Background: Black or your brand red
- Text: "ADD TO CART" in uppercase, white, bold
- Icon: Shopping bag (optional)
- Hover effect: slightly darker
- Click effect: subtle scale

**Wishlist Button:**
- Sits next to Add to Cart (20-25% width)
- Same height as Add to Cart
- Heart icon (outline when not saved, filled when saved)
- Border style to match
- Hover: shows background color

**Points/Rewards Info:**
Below the buttons, small text:
- "Earn up to 16 SHEIN Points calculated at checkout"
- With icon

### Collapsible Information Sections

**SHEIN does this very well:**

Below the action buttons, there are several collapsible sections. Each section has:
- A header row with: [Icon] [Title] [Chevron Down/Up]
- Clicking the header expands or collapses the content
- Smooth animation when expanding/collapsing
- Border between sections

**Shipping to [Country]:**
- Truck icon (green)
- Expanded shows:
  - "Free Shipping" badge
  - "Estimated delivery: Jan 27 - Feb 3"
  - Shipping provider info

**Return Policy:**
- Return arrow icon (blue)
- Expanded shows:
  - "Free Return"
  - "7 business days"
  - Terms link

**Shopping Security:**
- Shield icon (purple)
- Expanded shows:
  - "Safe Payments" with checkmark
  - "Privacy Protection" with checkmark
  - Additional security info

**Sourced from [Seller Name]:**
- Store icon (orange)
- Expanded shows:
  - "Sold by and Ships from [Seller]"
  - "Report this seller/product" link
  - Seller rating

### Additional Expandable Sections

**Description:**
- "Description" header with chevron
- Expanded shows:
  - Product tags: "Trends", "#ChicFWEdi", "Winter"
  - Full description text
  - Material and care information

**Size & Fit:**
- "Size & Fit" header with chevron
- Expanded shows:
  - Model measurements
  - Size recommendations
  - Fit guide

**About Store:**
- "About Store" header with chevron
- Expanded shows:
  - Seller card with logo and name
  - "Choice" or verified badge
  - Rating (e.g., "4.90")
  - Item count and follower count
  - User browsing indicator: "2K+ browsing now"
  - "All Items" button
  - "+ Follow" button

### Matching Styles Section (In Right Column)

**SHEIN shows this in the sticky sidebar:**

A section titled "Matching Styles" with a minimize option:
- Multiple categories:
  - "You May Like" (10 items)
  - "You May Love" (3 items)
  - "More Style" (1 item)
  - "Sets" (1 item)

Each shows a grid of products:
- 2-3 columns of product images
- Item count overlay
- Hover shows more info
- Click navigates to product or category

---

## FULL-WIDTH SECTIONS (Below Two-Column Layout)

After the two-column layout ends, the page continues with full-width sections.

### Customer Reviews Section

**IMPORTANT LAYOUT:**
This section uses a two-column layout again:
- Left column (55-60%): Reviews
- Right column (40-45%): Right sidebar content continues (About Store, Matching Styles)

**Left Column - Reviews:**

**Review Summary Card:**
- Large rating number: "4.55"
- 5 stars visualization
- Star count breakdown
- "Review Policy" link with info icon

**Fit Breakdown:**
- "Overall Fit:" title
- Three horizontal bars:
  - "Small (3%)" - short bar
  - "True to Size (87%)" - very long bar, prominent
  - "Large (10%)" - short bar

**Filter and Sort Bar:**
- "All Reviews" tab | "Image" tab
- Dropdown filters:
  - "Rating: All â–¼"
  - "Filter by product: All â–¼"
  - "Sort by: Recommend â–¼"

**Tag Filters:**
Horizontal row of filter chips:
- "No Smell (13)"
- "Good Portability (6)"
- "Keep Warm (6)"
- Active tags highlighted
- Counts in parentheses

**Review Cards:**
Each review card shows:
- User avatar (circular, 40-48px)
- Username (masked): "b***9"
- Date: "8 Oct, 2025"
- Star rating: 5 stars
- Product variant info: "Overall Fit: True to Size | Height: 186cm | Weight: 71kg | Size: L | Color: Beige"
- Review text (multiple lines)
- "Translate" link if foreign language
- Review images in a horizontal row (if any)
- Footer:
  - "From SHEIN US" text
  - "Points Program" badge
  - "Helpful (18)" button
  - "..." menu
- Border between reviews

**Pagination:**
At the bottom:
- Page numbers: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 ... 10
- Previous/Next arrows
- Centered

**Right Column (Continues):**
- The sticky sidebar content continues here
- Description (expandable)
- Size & Fit (expandable)
- About Store (expandable)
- Matching Styles gallery

### Customers Also Viewed Section

**Full-width section at the very bottom:**

**Title:** "Customers Also Viewed"

**Product Grid:**
- 5 columns on large desktop
- 4 columns on medium desktop
- 3 columns on tablets
- 16-20px gaps between products

**Product Card Structure:**

Each card shows:
- Product image (aspect ratio 3:4)
  - Badges on image (top-left):
    - "Trends" badge (purple)
    - "Choice" badge (black)
    - "#1 Bestseller in [Category]" (orange)
    - "#2 Bestseller", "#3 Bestseller"
    - Discount badge "-30%"
  - Wishlist heart icon (top-right)
  - Quick add cart icon (bottom-right circle, appears on hover)

- Below image:
  - Category tags (small badges)
  - Seller name with icon
  - Star rating + review count "(1000+)"
  - Original price (struck through, gray)
  - Sales count "2.0k+ sold" with fire icon
  - Current price (large, bold)
  - Special badges: "High Repeat Customers" (orange pill)

**Hover State:**
- Image zooms slightly
- Shadow increases
- Quick actions appear
- Smooth transition

**Bottom Action:**
- "View More" button (centered)
- Styled as outlined or subtle filled
- 200-250px wide, 44-48px tall

---

## STICKY BEHAVIOR DETAILS

**Right Sidebar Stickiness:**

**SHEIN does this:**
- The right column starts at the top of the page
- As you scroll down, it "sticks" and moves with the viewport
- It continues to stick until the bottom of the product information
- When you reach the reviews section, it stops sticking
- The reviews section then has its own two-column layout

**This allows:**
- Product info always visible while viewing images
- Easy access to Add to Cart while browsing
- Efficient use of screen space
- Natural reading flow

---

## INTERACTION BEHAVIORS

### Image Gallery
**Thumbnail Click:**
- Main image fades to new image (300ms transition)
- Clicked thumbnail gets red border
- Previous thumbnail loses border

**Main Image Hover:**
- Cursor changes to zoom icon
- Image zooms 120-150% on hover OR
- Magnifier glass appears showing zoomed detail

**Main Image Click:**
- Opens fullscreen lightbox
- Can navigate with arrow keys
- Can swipe on trackpad
- Close with X or Esc key

### Variant Selection
**Size Click:**
- Immediate visual feedback
- Selected state shows instantly
- Other sizes deselect
- Add to Cart enables if color also selected

**Color Click:**
- Same immediate feedback
- Main image might update to show that color
- Thumbnails might update to that color variant

**Out of Stock:**
- Size/color grayed out
- Cursor shows "not-allowed"
- Tooltip on hover: "Out of stock"

### Collapsible Sections
**Click Header:**
- Content expands/collapses smoothly
- Chevron rotates 180 degrees
- Smooth height transition (300ms)
- Can expand multiple sections at once OR accordion style (only one open)

### Add to Cart
**Click Button:**
- Shows loading state (spinner in button)
- Validation check (size and color selected?)
- If incomplete: highlight missing selections
- If complete: shows success state
- Cart badge in sidebar updates (+1)
- Toast notification: "Added to cart"

### Wishlist
**Click Heart:**
- Fills with color animation
- Shows toast: "Added to favorites"
- Persists on page reload

### Reviews
**Helpful Button:**
- Click increments count
- Button changes to "Thanked" or checkmark
- Cannot un-click
- Visual feedback

**Image Click:**
- Opens lightbox with all review images
- Can navigate through images
- Shows review text alongside

---

## VISUAL DESIGN SPECIFICATIONS

**Match Your Existing Laku Design:**

**Colors:**
- Use the EXACT same red for prices as your homepage
- Use the EXACT same gray for secondary text
- Product cards in recommendations should look IDENTICAL to homepage
- Same backgrounds (white)
- Same borders (subtle gray)
- Same shadows (if you use them)

**Typography:**
- Same font family throughout
- Product title: 24-28px bold
- Price: 36-40px bold
- Body text: 15-16px regular
- Small text: 13-14px regular

**Spacing:**
- Consistent padding in cards (20-24px)
- Consistent gaps between sections (32-48px)
- Consistent gaps in grids (16-20px)

**Borders and Shadows:**
- Subtle shadows on cards (if any)
- Light borders on inactive buttons
- Consistent border radius (8-12px on cards)

**Interactive States:**
- Hover: slight color change, subtle scale
- Active/Pressed: slight scale down (0.98)
- Disabled: 50% opacity, cursor not-allowed
- Loading: spinner, button disabled

---

## DESKTOP-SPECIFIC FEATURES

**Hover Effects:**
- Product cards: image zoom, shadow increase
- Buttons: color darken
- Thumbnails: border highlight
- Links: color change

**Keyboard Navigation:**
- Tab through interactive elements
- Enter to click buttons
- Arrow keys in image gallery (nice to have)
- Esc to close modals

**Mouse Interactions:**
- Smooth scrolling
- Hover previews
- Cursor changes (pointer, zoom, etc.)
- Smooth transitions (200-300ms)

---

## RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR

**Large Desktop (1400px+):**
- Max-width container for content
- 5 columns in product grid
- Comfortable spacing

**Medium Desktop (1200-1400px):**
- 4-5 columns in product grid
- Same layout structure
- Slightly tighter spacing

**Desktop (1024-1200px):**
- 3-4 columns in product grid
- Right sidebar might be 35-38% instead of 40%
- Still uses sticky behavior

**Tablet (768-1024px):**
- 3 columns in product grid
- Might reduce sidebar width to 30%
- Tighter spacing
- Smaller text sizes

---

## KEY REFERENCE LEARNINGS

**From SHEIN:**
- Perfect sticky sidebar implementation
- Excellent collapsible sections
- Clean, minimal design
- Great use of badges
- Smart color organization

**From Shopee:**
- Great seller information display
- Good review system
- Clear pricing hierarchy
- Effective recommendation sections

**From Amazon:**
- Clear product information hierarchy
- Trustworthy review system
- Good specification tables
- Effective cross-sells

---

## WHAT TO BUILD

Create a desktop product page that:
- Works WITHIN your existing Laku app layout (keeps your sidebar)
- Uses a two-column layout for product image and info
- Has a sticky right sidebar that stops at reviews
- Shows reviews in a two-column layout
- Displays "Customers Also Viewed" in a multi-column grid
- Matches your existing design system perfectly
- Feels professional and trustworthy
- Makes shopping easy with clear CTAs
- Provides all information customers need to make a decision

Focus on creating a clean, professional shopping experience that builds trust and makes purchasing straightforward. Every element should have a purpose and be easy to find and use.